text: Novokurmashevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Starokurmashevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 201 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Kushnarenkovo, 12 km from Starokurmashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Novokurmashevo
